==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pentamera
<hw>Pen*tam"e*ra</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[NL. See
<er>Pentamerous</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>An extensive
division of Coleoptera, including those that normally have five-jointed
tarsi. It embraces about half of all the known species of the
Coleoptera.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pentameran</ent>⟦br⟧
